member.remarks:
Minimal appsettings.json:

{
  "WhatsApp": {
    "PhoneNumberId": "1234567890",
    "AccessToken": "EAAxxxx...",
    "ApiVersion": "v23.0",
    "TimeoutSeconds": 30,
    "DefaultCountryCode": "593"
  }
}


Multi-tenant appsettings.json:

{
  "WhatsApp": {
    "Accounts": {
      "company-a": { "PhoneNumberId": "...", "AccessToken": "..." },
      "company-b": { "PhoneNumberId": "...", "AccessToken": "..." }
    }
  }
}

Then pass Credentials = WhatsAppCredentials.FromAccount("company-a") in your request.
